{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "霍普 第2话 想要守护他人的心意",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "敌人像这样砍过来时，\\n我这样避开，\\n然后回头的瞬间这样……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "霍普，别在祭坛拿着法杖挥来挥去，\\n你到底在做什么啊。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "啊……埃尔菲莉丝前辈！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "前、前辈！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "是的！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "我将来想放弃当什么祭司，\\n成为骑士。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "可能有些心急，\\n但你作为出色的骑士是我的目标，\\n所以才称呼你为前辈！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "对了。我刚才是在\\n想像实战情况，尝试应对！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "如何？还像样吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "比起这个……\\n你应该还有其他事要做吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "打扫祭坛，不是交给你负责了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "啊……那件事晚点再做。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "骑士的训练\\n重要得多。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "对了！埃尔菲莉丝前辈，\\n你作为骑士，是怎么训练的？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "请让我见识一下，我想作为参考！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "你是想以这个为借口，\\n逃避打扫吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "呜……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "真是的……你不是骑士，是祭司。\\n要好好完成自己的工作。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "可是，\\n祭司的工作就算做了，\\n也没什么意义吧？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "没有意义……\\n那是什么意思？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "祭司什么的，不是在传教时说一些漂亮话，\\n就是听人忏悔后，\\n讲一堆无聊的道理……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "净是这些事吧。\\n实际上根本没有任何帮助。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "我倒是……并不这么认为。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "我不想成为祭司。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "我更想成为……\\n能够守护别人的男人。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "我对于挥剑战斗、以身为盾，\\n都已经有觉悟了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "我想将我的生命，\\n用在守护别人上！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "……\\n这样啊。你有那样的心思，很了不起。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "但是霍普，连自己的工作\\n都无法好好完成的人，\\n我不认为能成为出色的骑士。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "呜……说的也是……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "既然埃尔菲莉丝前辈都这么说了……\\n虽然很麻烦，我还是会打扫的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "不过……\\n好吧，等你打扫完，\\n我可以陪你进行骑士训练。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "咦……\\n你、你说的，是真的吗！？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "是啊。因为你想要守护他人的心意，\\n似乎是真心实意的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "但是……你可别误会了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "你想放弃祭司、\\n成为骑士的目标，\\n我不赞成……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "谢谢你！\\n我马上把祭坛扫得干干净净！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110038_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "霍普",
            "context": "训练的事，就请你多多帮忙了！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "哎呀……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "看来，光用说的\\n无法阻止你对骑士的向往呢。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}